phred quality scores fastq key
	Given a character $sq, the following Perl code gives the Phred quality $Q: 
	$Q = 10 * log(1 + 10 ** (ord($sq) - 64) / 10.0)) / log(10);
	http://seqanswers.com/forums/showthread.php?t=2312
